frus:attachment.p:
14. To continue to build up and increase the air routes and air supplies to
                        China, and the development of facilities, with a view to:— 

                                a.

Keeping China in the war;

                                b.

Intensifying operations against the Japanese;

                                c.

Maintaining increased U.S. and Chinese air forces in China;

                                d.

Equipping Chinese ground forces.

Cross-channel operations (

        Overlord

).
